text: Chuvash-Ulkanovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Tatar-Ulkanovsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 158 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 9 km from Tuymazy, 3 km from Tatar-Ulkanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Chuvash-Ulkanovo
